Prometheus exporter for OPNsense metrics.

Runs a daemon that collects OPNsense-specific metrics and writes them in
Prometheus format to the node_exporter textfile collector directory.

Currently exports gateway metrics:
  opnsense_gateway_status        - numeric status (0=down, 1=up, 2=loss, 3=delay)
  opnsense_gateway_delay_seconds - round-trip time in seconds
  opnsense_gateway_stddev_seconds - RTT standard deviation in seconds
  opnsense_gateway_loss_ratio    - packet loss ratio (0.0-1.0)
  opnsense_gateway_info          - informational metric with status/monitor labels

WWW: https://github.com/brendanbank/opnsense-metrics-exporter
